{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"測試 media queries","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Testing_media_queries","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>這是一個實驗中的功能</strong><br>此功能在某些瀏覽器尚在開發中，請參考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">兼容表格</a>以得到不同瀏覽器用的前輟。</p></div>\n<p>DOM 提供了一個用程式去測試 media query 的方法：那就是透過 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a> 物件；透過 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a> 物件上的屬性和方法，我們可以得知、觀察目前 media query 的狀態。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"創建_media_query_list_物件","title":"創建 media query list 物件","isH3":false,"content":"<p>透過傳入目標 medai query 到 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia\"><code>window.matchMedia</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 方法，我們將可以取得相對應的 MediaQueryList 物件。</p>\n<p>以下範例將取得偵測螢幕方向的 MediaQueryList 物件：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">var mql = window.matchMedia(\"(orientation: portrait)\");\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"檢查_media_query_結果","title":"檢查 media query 結果","isH3":false,"content":"<p>讀取 MediaQueryList 物件 的 matches 屬性就可以得知測試結果：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mql<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>matches<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* The device is currently in portrait orientation */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* The device is currently in landscape orientation */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"接收測試結果通知","title":"接收測試結果通知","isH3":false,"content":"<p>當我們想要動態依據 media query 測試狀況執行對應處理，除了持續定期偵測外，還有一個更有效率的途徑：那就是註冊 media query 的事件處理器 (listener)。只要呼叫 MediaQueryList 物件上 addListener 方法，傳入符合 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryListListener</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 介面的 listener 便完成事件註冊：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> mql <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchMedia</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"(orientation: portrait)\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmql<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>handleOrientationChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">handleOrientationChange</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mql<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>上面我們替螢幕方向 media query 註冊了一個 listener。請注意，在第一次註冊後，listener 會立刻被呼叫一次，這是為了初始化準備，因為我們可能預設 UI 是針對 'portait' 模式，但目前卻是 'landscape' 模式，所以這個第一次呼叫將給予我們作初始化調整的空間。</p>\n<p><code>下面handleOrientationChange()</code> 方法便是我們針對螢幕方向變化的 listener：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">handleOrientationChange</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">mql</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mql<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>matches<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/* The device is currently in portrait orientation */</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/* The device is currently in landscape orientation */</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"停止接收測試結果通知","title":"停止接收測試結果通知","isH3":false,"content":"<p>當我們不需要接受通知時，只需要呼叫 removeListener 方法，然後傳入欲移除的 listener 即可：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">mql.removeListener(handleOrientationChange);\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaQueryList","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Testing_media_queries/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"延伸閱讀","title":"延伸閱讀","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Media queries (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia\"><code>window.matchMedia()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryListListener</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"創建 media query list 物件","id":"創建_media_query_list_物件"},{"text":"檢查 media query 結果","id":"檢查_media_query_結果"},{"text":"接收測試結果通知","id":"接收測試結果通知"},{"text":"停止接收測試結果通知","id":"停止接收測試結果通知"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"},{"text":"延伸閱讀","id":"延伸閱讀"}],"summary":"DOM 提供了一個用程式去測試 media query 的方法：那就是透過 MediaQueryList 物件；透過 MediaQueryList 物件上的屬性和方法，我們可以得知、觀察目前 media query 的狀態。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Testing media queries programmatically","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Tester les requêtes média en JavaScript","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"プログラムによるメディアクエリーの評価","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Тестирование медиавыражений программно","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"使用编程方法测试媒体查询","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/css/media_queries/testing_media_queries","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/css/media_queries/testing_media_queries/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries","title":"Media queries"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Testing_media_queries","title":"測試 media queries"}],"pageTitle":"測試 media queries - CSS | MDN","noIndexing":false}}